Ejecutar Kubernetes
1. Dockenizamos los servicios
docker build -t usuarios:latest /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/usuarios
docker build -t catalogo:latest /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/catalogo
docker build -t orders:latest /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/orders
docker build -t payments:latest /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/payments
docker build -t entregas:latest /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/entregas

2. Desplegar los ms
kubectl apply -k /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/k8s
kubectl get pods -n pedidos-dev -w

3. Ver estados
kubectl get all -n pedidos-dev

4. Para exponer por port forward
kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev svc/usuarios 8082:8082
kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev svc/catalogo 8083:8083
kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev svc/orders 8084:8084
kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev svc/payments 8085:8085
kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev svc/entregas 8086:8086


5. Monitoreo
kubectl logs -n pedidos-dev deployment/orders -f
kubectl logs -n pedidos-dev deployment/payments -f
kubectl logs -n pedidos-dev deployment/entregas -f


6. Eliminar
kubectl delete -k /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/k8s

7. Limpiar imagenes
docker rmi usuarios:latest catalogo:latest orders:latest payments:latest entregas:latest


8. Para levantar porforward

- Dar permisos: chmod +x /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/port-forward.sh
/Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/port-forward.sh

- Ejecutar: /Users/joelampuero/Documents/Learning/Tecsup/ms/port-forward.sh

- Detener: pkill -f "kubectl port-forward -n pedidos-dev"

- Verificar si estan activos: ps aux | grep "kubectl port-forward"

- Logs: cat /tmp/ms-port-forward/orders.log
cat /tmp/ms-port-forward/payments.log

